To record clips to tracks in [[Ableton Live]] do these things.

'''1.''' Click the record button.



[[File:Click and turn on record button.png]]



'''2.''' Launch the clip or scene you wish to convert to track(s).
You can launch various clips and scenes in real-time and Ableton Live will record them as audio tracks.
If you wish the [[Ableton Live:Creating warped loops|clips to loop]] or [[Ableton:Launch box|play in a particular manner]] you must set up the appropriate parameters. 


